been 'spooked' by the amount of paparazzi waiting outside the 
Morningside Recovery in Newport Beach, and refused to check into the 
facility.

Lohan was said to have then 'begged' Holley to return as her lawyer after prosecutors said they would seek an arrest warrant if the star was not back in rehab by sunrise on Friday, reported TMZ.

Lohan was allegedly unimpressed with the way lawyer Mark Heller
had handled her case, and spent the better part of Thursday convincing 
Holley to return after she sensationally fired her last year.

'Lindsay cannot stand [Heller] and thinks he doesn’t know what he is doing,' a source told RadarOnline.com. 'So late Thursday, from hiding, she began calling and emailing Shawn incessantly.

